name: IT Master Services
overview:
We provide professional computer repair services, website development and design services, and other computer related services in Reno-Sparks, Nevada. We are here to assist with all your computer service and website development and design needs. We will work with you to make sure you know exactly what you are getting when it comes to any of our computer services and website development and design services. We believe in up front and honest computer repair services, website development services and other computer services, we are your local reliable and dedicated computer services and website development and design company. Whether it’s a simple computer repair or and advanced computer service or website development or design services, we are here to help you better leverage technology in your home and business environments.

Our computer repairs and computer services include: computer virus removal, computer repair services (computer reformats, hardware replacements, etc.), data recovery services, data backup services and website design and development services and Microsoft Online Services.
